spec_data.Name: guichan
spec_data.Description:
Guichan is a small, efficient C++ GUI library designed for games. It comes
with a standard set of widgets and can use several different objects for
displaying graphics and grabbing user input.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 03 Aug 2017 10:07:31 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Portable C++ GUI library for games using Allegro, SDL and OpenGL
